reviewText: Love this one in a darkened room!
This is just what I was looking for! Excellent to have playing in the kitchen when I'm cooking! The seller even included an additional DVD as a gift! Thank you!!
This was so very disappointing, I can not believe I purchased this, I just through money away.  I am a Ashtanga Practitioner and this is so beneath me.
This DVD has become my calming candle-light for yoga / reading / or just a chance to relax at the end of the evening.

The candles were lame and there was no way to turn off the dreadful 'music'.  They should re-title this "Mood Ruiner 2000".

Why doesn't someone just shoot these in High-def?

Avoid this one at all costs.
I watch a lot of relaxation/ meditational dvds and this is one of my favorites! very mesmerizing

After a tragedy or hard emotional times you need to find things that can help you find comfort, relaxation and help you sleep. My friend bought me this DVD and it really helps, I put it on and let it play as I potter around the house at night and wind down. Great also if you want something to help you fall asleep, with the candle light luminance and not worry about burning the house down.
absolutely relaxing tool with the soundtrack!  turn the soundtrack off...and it turns into a great visual!  great price too!  very good.
